subject: Olympic Games (2008)
Track and Field
Running
lead_paragraph: By day, Lesley Higgins works as a compliance director on Gov. David Paterson’s campaign staff. But Thursday night, she’ll be competing for a spot on the 2008 Olympic team in steeplechase.
